sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    
    participant S as Sensors
    participant E as ESP32
    participant M as NanoMQ
    participant B as Backend
    participant ML as ML Service
    participant D as Dashboard
    
    Note over S,E: Sensing Phase
    loop Every 1 second
        S->>E: ADC Read (GPIO34, GPIO35)
        E->>E: RMS Calculation (200 samples)
        E->>E: Power = V × I
        E->>E: Energy += P × dt
        E->>E: Update OLED Display
    end
    
    Note over E,M: Transmission Phase
    E->>M: MQTT Publish<br>energy/device01/telemetry
    M-->>E: ACK (QoS 1)
    
    Note over M,B: Backend Processing
    M->>B: Forward Message
    B->>B: Parse JSON
    B->>B: Append to CSV
    
    Note over B,ML: ML Analysis
    B->>ML: check_anomaly(reading)
    ML->>ML: Z-score calculation
    ML->>ML: Isolation Forest predict
    ML-->>B: is_anomaly: true/false
    
    alt Anomaly Detected
        B->>B: Log anomaly
        B->>D: SSE Push (anomaly event)
        D->>D: Show Alert Toast
    end
    
    Note over B,D: Dashboard Update
    B->>D: SSE Push (telemetry)
    D->>D: Update Gauges
    D->>D: Update Chart
    
    Note over D,B: User Control
    D->>B: POST /relay {on: true}
    B->>M: MQTT Publish<br>energy/device01/relay/set
    M->>E: Relay Command
    E->>E: relay.value(0)
    E->>M: MQTT Publish<br>energy/device01/relay/state
    M->>B: Forward State
    B->>D: SSE Push (relay state)
    
    Note over D,ML: ML Prediction Request
    D->>B: GET /ml/predict/fridge
    B->>ML: predict_power("fridge")
    ML->>ML: Load model
    ML->>ML: Extract features
    ML->>ML: LightGBM predict
    ML-->>B: {predicted_power: 85.3}
    B-->>D: JSON Response
    D->>D: Display Prediction
